  "short_description": "In this vertical precision platformer, run, jump, and climb your way through challenging obstacles with satisfying and tight controls. Navigate through atmospheric terrarium vegetation and uncover hidden paths. Perfect for fans of skill-based platformers, every fall is your fault!",
