  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Climb to the top!</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275480/extras/9b862b5061b3119e902cf1acc8ed3033.poster.avif?t=1746467243\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275480/extras/9b862b5061b3119e902cf1acc8ed3033.webm?t=1746467243\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275480/extras/9b862b5061b3119e902cf1acc8ed3033.mp4?t=1746467243\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Green Heights is a first person vertical precision platformer with smooth and satisfying movement. Set in a unique terrarium like environment climb the tower and reach the top.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Get back on your feet<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275480/extras/2c47085a299a62936b0871c2eb77cc86.poster.avif?t=1746467243\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275480/extras/2c47085a299a62936b0871c2eb77cc86.webm?t=1746467243\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275480/extras/2c47085a299a62936b0871c2eb77cc86.mp4?t=1746467243\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Falling down is inevitable, every mistake is a lesson learned that you can use to climb even faster. Lots of shortcut are available in the tower, discover them to beat your personal best!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275480/extras/9d8eb4439dedb913cd3f00351e487c28.poster.avif?t=1746467243\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275480/extras/9d8eb4439dedb913cd3f00351e487c28.webm?t=1746467243\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275480/extras/9d8eb4439dedb913cd3f00351e487c28.mp4?t=1746467243\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fluid and responsive movement</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Atmospheric terrarium vegetation</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run, Jumps, climb and bounce your way to the top</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover shortcut</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leaderboard</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Personal best time Ghost racing</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Climb to the top!</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275480/extras/9b862b5061b3119e902cf1acc8ed3033.poster.avif?t=1746467243\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275480/extras/9b862b5061b3119e902cf1acc8ed3033.webm?t=1746467243\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275480/extras/9b862b5061b3119e902cf1acc8ed3033.mp4?t=1746467243\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Green Heights is a first person vertical precision platformer with smooth and satisfying movement. Set in a unique terrarium like environment climb the tower and reach the top.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Get back on your feet<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275480/extras/2c47085a299a62936b0871c2eb77cc86.poster.avif?t=1746467243\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275480/extras/2c47085a299a62936b0871c2eb77cc86.webm?t=1746467243\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275480/extras/2c47085a299a62936b0871c2eb77cc86.mp4?t=1746467243\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Falling down is inevitable, every mistake is a lesson learned that you can use to climb even faster. Lots of shortcut are available in the tower, discover them to beat your personal best!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275480/extras/9d8eb4439dedb913cd3f00351e487c28.poster.avif?t=1746467243\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275480/extras/9d8eb4439dedb913cd3f00351e487c28.webm?t=1746467243\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275480/extras/9d8eb4439dedb913cd3f00351e487c28.mp4?t=1746467243\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fluid and responsive movement</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Atmospheric terrarium vegetation</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run, Jumps, climb and bounce your way to the top</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover shortcut</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leaderboard</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Personal best time Ghost racing</p></li></ul>",
